{"tid":1787802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】何謂黃店／黃色經濟圈？","createTime":"2019-12-18T07:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T01:35:38.000Z","uid":35364,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd0cdd204077a9ba375d282227d740d4924a54f","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"　　　　　　　　黃色經濟圈，大家都同意要招攬更多店鋪加入，但問題在於要招攬咩店鋪加入，以及點樣先叫「黃店」？<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　　　　要定義「黃店」必須要釐清黃色經濟圈的目標，否則無法釐訂合適標準與門檻。黃色經濟圈不外乎兩個目標：<strong>其一，與魔警、藝人、藍店割蓆，向政府製造輿論壓力，杯葛極深藍的店鋪，使深藍儘快歸西</strong>。要達到上述目標，自然要招攬更多店鋪加盟。因此，不管店主本人有何想法，總之公司願意出聲明譴責警暴，以後不再支持政府與魔警，就可以前事不計。這類型黃店的功能本身就是割蓆，所以明確表態是必要條件。<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　　　　藍店想賺錢就要清晰表態，不能好似達迖、Ming 仔咁含糊其詞。<strong>任何藍店想轉黃店，必須親自發出投降聲明，不能由知名人士代勞，否則將來有事可能會變鵪鶉，側側膊當無事發生</strong>。沒有討價還價的空間，表態已經是最低要求。上述要求只適用於口頭撐警的藍色小店。<strong>有實際行動撐警的深藍集團，必須有具體行動彌補過錯</strong>，例如去聯合國抹黑運動的美心集團，必須開國際記者會向公眾道歉，我們才會考慮接納對方。門檻不應過高，但不應過低，始終牠們曾經傷害過手足，總不能一下子就完全放下心防。做戲要做全套，如果證據確鑿變返藍，我相信大家會知道點做。<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　　　　另一類黃店目標係實際支援運動，如聘請手足、捐款捐物資、法律支援，諸如此類。不是口頭參與，而是實際參與者，<strong>其營運邏輯是自給自足：支持抗爭的消費者去幫襯，然後店主將一部份營利重新投入運動，以保障抗爭可以持續進行</strong>。由於大多數人將兩類黃店混為一談（包括沈旭暉在內），以至於標準與門檻往往各有不同。沈旭暉在評論文章問道：‧「『黃店』的飲食貨源大部份來自中國，是否都是『扮黃』？」如果定義清楚是哪一種黃店，這個問題不難回答。實際上，參與運動的第二類黃店，目標絕非與藍店斷絕交易來往，而在於將一部分資金再度投入運動。這類黃店首要目標是幫助手足，而不在於杯葛藍絲與藍店。如同沈旭暉所言，這類黃店可透過「表藍內黃」的方式營運，但暫時仍未有類似的黃店浮上水面（可能是靜靜雞），大多都是兩類兼備、俗稱「黃到金」的店鋪。<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　　　　　兩種黃店的運作型態完全不同，偏偏習慣混為一談，口同鼻拗。如同和理非與勇武各有功能，輿論壓力與實際支援，兩者不可偏廢。第一類黃店提供<strong>商業網絡，將來有潛力發展為「黃色生產鏈」</strong>，第二類黃店直接支持抗爭，是黃色經濟圈的靈魂所在。關鍵不在於是否建立分級制，而在於是否了解背後的功能與原理。任何黃店必須發揮其應有的功能，否則黃色經濟圈只會徒有虛名。明白黃店都係做生意，門檻唔可以太高，但亦不能無門檻。無表態咪當中立，行過無得選擇先幫襯，係咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　　　　　最後想講一點，監察黃店／知名人士係天公地道。唔好動不動就話手足係「紅衛兵」，話人「捉鬼」、「分化」、「批鬥」。叫人唔好分化，但又主動貶低人地。既然大家都係為件事，講野有返基本禮貌，唔好因為未表態的外人而內部分化。我亦想趁機向各位 KOL 呼籲：由於你地有影響力，講野最好都控一控制自己，<strong>諗一諗身分與時機係咪恰當，修飾一下言辭，講野係咪要咁盡</strong>。雖然五毛係咪都會分化，但無理由自己參與埋一份。講完。"},{"pid":"fbdb31f274869530b71ce18e69b2f385b28082fa","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af15053bae70d3a5c6d774c50ab2bebf7d2e77c3","tid":1787802,"uid":97120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又話年宵係黃色經濟圈核彈<br />\n要檔主！ 要香港人！<br />\n幫手推post！<br />\n<br />\n［代post] 觀塘年宵見接受檔主申請啦！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785576</a><br />\n<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a901cae28e8bd58c2eaf840185737220a8b0725","tid":1787802,"uid":43468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"反而我諗為要界定咩係籃店<br />\n黃金經濟圈（唔好再用黃色經濟圈，有黃色事業意思，唔怕生壞命最怕改錯名）目的係唔好再比中共賺外匯，而籃店除左係支持班狗外，我認為最重要係比大陸賺錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要中共加速玩完，就唔好俾佢賺外匯"},{"pid":"729059ebff6f4df6e3a110bdac3eef047adf5e99","tid":1787802,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"門口寫黑警死全家就得"},{"pid":"bef52785906e31398967f544092d20fd521ea588","tid":1787802,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6b0dd6605f0ee78c5dd59cc3b0ebf5bcaabc7e","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113701c09f13ce6a3d2bd7d3c435c1c23959c96","tid":1787802,"uid":288678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114f52ede28be22983a43b14e3c095feb1d0985b","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e3f6bd1688121f64574ed962fc30c9dcd6c417","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5e6638de1ac4c7a9aad8f1dc16ecaca33e7fcf","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9df20085aefd5ca0abf669415a5cf8216dd7f1","tid":1787802,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"黑警與綠曱甴不得內進"},{"pid":"1ccbdc7f0374180768701e5faf9f365ae4f81aee","tid":1787802,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0816f9fc3fa8b63f51376eeb1184f017f81300cb","tid":1787802,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ed54e87ba2b2576a88d63c70a92cdab7e2077d0f","tid":1787802,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42003a7de5cf75059c80c214467b8d718e886b1f","tid":1787802,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟圈】無需分級，加評分同推薦就得<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787642</a>"},{"pid":"df4cf7fad0192cc2326d1990f92ac79b074221a1","tid":1787802,"uid":259520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"點解中共會介意黃色經濟圈??<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1776083/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1776083/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n個人認為,唔好迫商人表態,<br />\n容許佢地只做生意,唔理政治.<br />\n迫商家只會令商家反感."},{"pid":"37a12ba0d03d0f4668cd52ca277984f56eaa580a","tid":1787802,"uid":284597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a256fd2f5920a882332ff9e51e1b66d5116f44c7","tid":1787802,"uid":273057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ce442ac38692d494b4ff48408ea55a3656bdfa","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"無人睇就算，讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a5dc3b8fea08fa7fc65e01da9455e812c1ac39","tid":1787802,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac8845c8cb05280982d84ff406e21694ed8616e5","tid":1787802,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3087a8eb9c0574f85736863e603ebceed600a05","tid":1787802,"uid":326427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"同意！"},{"pid":"2066a692d77d50cc0ba6466853502b5d88ab62b1","tid":1787802,"uid":181649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"推, 其實某程度扮黃都無所謂, 一樣有興論效果, 而且搞搞下會兩面不是人, 一係就仲衰過之前, 一係就要繼續黃落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44fbb7c15c4ea2e0578ca0c9b50b23de6e66a8d","tid":1787802,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"fea8511728ceac8dcebf406be20763aeb76edf5c","tid":1787802,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"沈旭輝提出咗一個問題：<br />\n點先可以形成地下商業網絡？<br />\n估計第一階段係無法做到，<br />\n要中共打壓先有機會做得到。<br />\n<br />\n就算你自稱係黃，話想幫手，<br />\n貿貿然咁樣自薦，必有戒心。<br />\n情況等同人地已經組好隊，<br />\n唔會上到前線先亂咁加人。<br />\n除非真係落單，需要人幫手。<br />\n<br />\n譬如加租／斷貨源缺隊友，<br />\n表藍暗黃就有機會主動幫手。<br />\n業主只需要承諾唔會加租，<br />\n供應商寫明批貨有事會賠償。<br />\n用在商言商做藉口就過到骨。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔需要表明政治立場，<br />\n日久見人心，慢慢有地下網絡，<br />\n以後只需要靠過來人推薦，<br />\n唔需要依靠任何大台認證系統。<br />\n<br />\n不過，沈生講到咩金融之類，<br />\n跨國企業同示威綑綁等同豪賭，<br />\n難度未免太高，唔到我地話事。<br />\n扮中立暗中出手，已經係極限。<br />\n<br />\n攬炒後，經濟圈都未免頂得順。<br />\n如果仲視經濟攬炒為目標的話，<br />\n請各位記住經濟圈只係過渡階段，<br />\n終極目標係置之死地而後生。"}}